metadata.name: Not Without You - by Dario De Siena
metadata.description:
With this piece i like to show my appreciation to all my supporter in the last 2 years in my NFT journey. I'm blessed and forever thankful for the hug change you all brought to my life.  


As an artist, being able to be free and create without fear is the most valuable thing for me. It gives me the power to create and push to the next level without thinking about stopping. Thank you all for being a big or small part in my artist journey.

Much Love Dario
